title: Remember Election Day on 11/3; Early Voting Ends 10/29 (Sagadahoc County Democratic Committee)
text: ( Source : Sagadahoc County Democratic Committee) We have an important election coming up right here and now, so please remember to cast your vote in the statewide Referendum Election Tuesday, November 3 , 2015 . Early voting ends Thursday,
